column1: Baby Barnaby's////I came here today with my mom. I woulda given them 5 stars
column2: but the wait was about 45 mins for inside seating
column3: the other option is on the patio.  I had the greens eggs with smoked apple chicken sausage
column4: hash browns and toast. It was delicious! The eggs are a little mushy due to the spinach
column5: but nothing to complain about.  While here
column6: you should definitely try the fresh squeezed orange juice!
